{"tid":633414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件無意得做得好啱嘅事","createTime":"2018-04-18T09:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T18:07:01.000Z","uid":129521,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f61d646ad07225402b25ad01069a4c2ae7216363","tid":633414,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:51:16.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想當年讀小學嗰陣有個好好嘅朋友。有一次同佢出街玩，當時佢嫲嫲入咗醫院一排 我哋喺條街準備去唔知邊到玩嘅時候，突然佢屋企人打俾佢叫佢去醫院探嫲嫲  但係佢想同我去玩多啲，咁佢屋企人就俾佢揀去玩定探嫲嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢問我咁點呀，我答佢：去探嫲嫲啦，我哋幾時都有得玩，咁跟著佢就番去同屋企人探嫲嫲  。<br />\n  到第二日我打比佢叫佢出嚟玩佢話佢嫲嫲走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢去到探嫲嫲嘅時候嫲嫲已經好虛弱，好似見完我朋友交低幾句遺言就去咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n   真係好好彩叫咗佢講去探嫲嫲 平時我係好貪玩嘅人，如果佢去同我玩而錯失見嫲嫲最後一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我真係會內疚一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5382ae9e436dd74d5cedebee9629772cc6eb51","tid":633414,"uid":9566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"無 無意做錯事就大把"},{"pid":"11bb06e1aba88dce253a994d3d5a3627ab819fd9","tid":633414,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b5382ae9e436dd74d5cedebee9629772cc6eb51","tid":633414,"uid":9566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"無 無意做錯事就大把"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"Ching 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a316e508e4adf6d7169693580c75683808995ae","tid":633414,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11bb06e1aba88dce253a994d3d5a3627ab819fd9","tid":633414,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b5382ae9e436dd74d5cedebee9629772cc6eb51","tid":633414,"uid":9566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"sco